videos.description: Kelan Martin throws the three-quarters court outlet pass to Tyler Wideman for the layup.
videos.headline: Butler's Martin throws the perfect outlet pass

videos.description: Steon Hall's Myles Powell splashes in the catch-and-shoot 3-pointer on the fast break.
videos.headline: Powell knocks down the transition three for the Pirates

videos.description: Seton Hall's Desi Rodriguez comes off the bench after returning from injury to help surge the offense for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Rodriquez knocks down the three

videos.description: Seton Hall's Myles Powell finds Desi Rodriguez for the layup after the Pirates move the ball around with ease.
videos.headline: Pirates' great ball movement leads to the easy bucket

videos.description: After colliding with a Butler player and falling to the ground, Seton Hall's Angel Delgado gets up, collects himself and finishes with the strong dunk.
videos.headline: Delgado goes to the ground but still dunks it

videos.description: After a missed shot from Jordan Walker, Butler gets the rebound and sends the ball downcourt, which allows Henry Baddley to get the basket.
videos.headline: Butler's great hustle gives them the lead

videos.description: With the clock winding down, Butler's Kamar Baldwin drives and knocks down the fadeaway shot to help the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Baldwin fades away for the jumper

videos.description: With less than 15 seconds to go and down a point, Butler's Tyler Wideman takes it downcourt and lays it in to lift the Bulldogs over the Pirates.
videos.headline: Butler's game winner is a thriller
